title: 820-2936 run slow with battery
message:
When only with battery, it runs slowly.

HS_OTHER_IOUT - 1.27V
PBUS_S0_VSENSE - 0V ??
PBUSVSENS_EN_L - 11.17V

I replaced Q5300 and U5410 as they were corroded. Could be something more?

VP0R pbus test

title: 820-2936 run slow with battery
message: PBUS_S0_VSENSE 0V is of course not correct and should give an error in ASD too. Something wrong with Q5300 or corroded traces.
